      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>GROSS-Ruth. On May 10, 2000. Beloved wife of the late Stewart. Loving mother of Fred, Alan and Paula. Dear sister of Harriet and the late Doris. Adoring grandmother of Stephanie and Samuel. Loving companion of Leonard Sherman. She will be profoundly missed. Service Sunday 11:45 AM at ''The Riverside'',76 Street and Amsterdam Avenue.</p>
